                    <span>Was sold at my bookstore. For those of you unawear, bias does exist and to prove it ask yourself this: How was the coverage of Bush's nationalguard days treated differently from Kerry's bouts with the Swift boat Vets? Would the New York Times try to smear 260 Guardsmen if they turned on Bush? And last what do you think about many editors stating that they would not have even covered the story if it were'nt for cable news and blogers?
